<div id="readme">
<h2>Doki Doki Kittytown</h2>
<ul>

<li><strong>Use the mouse to pick your actions!</strong> </li>
<li></li>

<li><strong>High Concept:</strong>
Try and win the heart of the kitty!
</li>

<li><strong>Player Experience Goals:</strong>
I want player to crave the kitty's love!
</li>

<li><strong>Genre:</strong>
This game is a Dating Sim.
</li>

<li><strong>Game play:</strong>
Simply click which actions you wish to do or which phrases you wish to say.
</li>

<li><strong>Prototype goal:</strong>
Figuring out how to make dating sim type games! :D
</li>

<li><strong>Features:</strong>
A dating sim! No action or enemies! Enjoy the hormones.
</li>

<li><strong>Setting/Premise:</strong>
You are a dead cat that is trying to escape from the land of the dead.
</li>

<li><strong>Story:</strong>
You are a dead cat. Since your death 40 years ago, your soul had no existance for
souls can only exist in the memories of the living. In other words, you died alone
and forgotten. However, you suddenly find yourself in the land of the dead, where
the souls of the remembered roam. Who possibly could have you in their memory? 
Unfortunately, cats aren't supposed to be in the land of the dead, for unknown reasons. 
The ghostly guards want you out and you agree with them. You want to find whoever
has remembered you, and your only chance is to visit the land of the living.
Luckily, there's a portal nearby for you to escape in!
</li>

<li><strong>Target Audience:</strong>
People into romance visual novel games.
</li>

<li><strong>Play time:</strong>
About two minutes.
</li>

<li><strong>Strategies:</strong>
Choose what you say and do carefully! Kitty will let you know if you're doing good
or not by the reactions.

</li>

<li><strong>Prototype Assets:</strong>
Main menu picture:http://znak.at.ua/_ph/7/743075919.jpg
Schoolroom: http://watchdog.org/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/2013/01/Japanese_high_school_classroom.jpg
</li>

<li><strong>Prototype Closest Other Game:</strong>
None.
</li>

</ul>
</div>
</body>
</html>
